{"tha-ap299:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap299:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap299:0.3":"7 Desakittakattheraapadana ","tha-ap299:1.1":"“Upasalakanamoham, ","tha-ap299:1.2":"ahosim brahmano tada; ","tha-ap299:1.3":"Kananam vanamogalham, ","tha-ap299:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap299:2.1":"Disvana vandim padesu, ","tha-ap299:2.2":"lokahutipatiggaham; ","tha-ap299:2.3":"Pasannacittam mam natva, ","tha-ap299:2.4":"buddho antaradhayatha. ","tha-ap299:3.1":"Kanana abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap299:3.2":"buddhasetthamanussarim; ","tha-ap299:3.3":"Tam desam kittayitvana, ","tha-ap299:3.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap299:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap299:4.2":"yam desamabhikittayim; ","tha-ap299:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap299:4.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap299:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap299:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap299:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap299:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma desakittako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap299:7.1":"Desakittakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}